asset.hookText:
Hi Gali, I read your review on Amazon.com and have a good idea of what's going on. It's always best to make sure that your Air Steerable is set for "floor" mode for best pick up performance. I put together this quick video for you to show you how to change modes and included steps on how to use the tools. Let me know if you need any more help!

-Wil
